title: Our Lawn Improvement with Lawn Pride
text:
We formerly used different lawn care company, but every year the lawn kept getting worse!!  We finally started looking around our neighbors yards to see which ones looked the best!!  We finally were able to see some yards that had the little Lawn Pride flags in them, and we are so glad we changed to Lawn Pride!!

Lawn Pride took care of the areas in our yard where grass had stopped growing!!

Lawn Pride didn’t skip over areas that were hard to reach….and we know they didn’t skip those areas, because thistle that used to grow there is now gone!!

Our lawn is now thicker and greener and without weeds anywhere!!  Thank you Lawn Pride for giving us a beautiful lawn!!

Sincerely,

William S Harnedy & Barbara Harnedy
